1931;;Mischief;;British;;Jack Raymond;;Ralph Lynn, Winifred Shotter;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mischief_(1931_film);;When financier Reginald Bingham leaves on a business trip to Paris, normally devoted wife Eleanor leaves for a cottage with a secret boy friend. The couple are followed by friends of her husband, who attempt to hinder the affair. However, Reginald is also tempted by a fling with an old friend in Paris.